   </settings>
   <cells rows="3" cols="1" cellWidth="500.0" cellHeight="90.0" border="true" id="primary">
    <style margin="4" borderStroke="0.7" markerStroke="5.0">
     <font family="Arial" size="20" />
     <color background="0xFFFFFF" inactive="0xFFFFFF" />
    </style>
    <shaper class="@Rectangular" cols="1" rows="3" />
    <cell id="0" avoidOverlapping="true" image="vert_rana.png">
     <p>Rana — tiene piel húmeda y vive en agua y tierra.</p>
     <media type="PLAY_AUDIO" level="1" file="ref_rana.mp3" />
    </cell>
    <cell id="1" avoidOverlapping="true" image="vert_delfin.png">
     <p>Delfín — nace del vientre de su madre y respira aire.</p>
     <media type="PLAY_AUDIO" level="1" file="ref_delfin.mp3" />
    </cell>
    <cell id="0" avoidOverlapping="true" image="vert_serpiente.png">
     <p>Serpiente — tiene escamas y pone huevos en la tierra.</p>
     <media type="PLAY_AUDIO" level="1" file="ref_serpiente.mp3" />
    </cell>
   </cells>
   <cells rows="3" cols="1" cellWidth="50.0" cellHeight="30.0" border="true" id="solvedPrimary">
    <style />
    <shaper class="@Rectangular" cols="1" rows="3" />
    <cell />
    <cell image="i01-bienhecho.jpg" />
    <cell />
   </cells>
   <scramble times="31" primary="true" />
  </activity>
